                              <div class="bg-dark rounded-circle text-white d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center" style="width: 50px; height: 50px; min-width: 50px;">3</div>
                              <div class="ms-3">
                                <h5>July 2025: Full Enforcement Begins</h5>
                                <p class="mb-0">Law enforcement agencies begin issuing citations for unregistered cyclists and those without proper insurance documentation.</p>
                              </div>
                            </div>
